### Check server status
GET http://localhost:8080

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/user

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/user/1

### Create a new user with JSON body
POST http://localhost:8080/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice"
}

### Search users with query params
GET http://localhost:8080/user?non=Existent&search=Jacob

### Search users with no matches
GET http://localhost:8080/user?search=nonexistent
